About Us
Novocall is an inbound sales automation startup. We help businesses that sells high-value products to increase their sales conversions by reducing response time.

We are supporting businesses from more than 2,000 businesses across 42 countries, and we are one of the highest rated callback software on platforms like Product Hunt and Capterra.
What we're looking for
[Traineeship] Digital Marketing Executive
Your role is help the marketing team to drive and execute successful marketing campaigns to acquire more customers.&nbsp;
Your Qualifications
We're looking for someone who is

  Bachelor's Degree in marketing related majors
  Experience in content marketing (Content creation, and content distribution)
  Knows and is familiar with SEO
  Excellent writer - you'll need to craft compelling copies and communicate well with users
  You're self-motivated and can't wait to prove yourself
  You're a fast learner and picks things up quickly
  Preferred: 1-2 year of work experience in a marketing or content marketing role (internship considered)
  Preferred: Experience working/interning in SaaS or technology companies

Your Responsibilities

  Execute&nbsp;Novocall's go-to-market strategy to drive acquisition and drive launches for our product
  Help with Novocall's product positioning and messaging through market research, user insights, and product understanding
  Optimize Novocall's digital marketing funnel and customer acquisition channels
  Work with team to drive company shared results - track the right metrics and execute campaigns that drive awareness and adoption

What you'll get

  You want to contribute heavily to a company and see actual results
  Joining a rocketship company with fast month-on-month growth
  You find personal growth a priority in your career
  Flexible working hours
  Remote work (WFH)

Eligibility Criteria for SGUnitedTraineeships

  Singapore Citizen or Permanent Resident;
  Graduated or graduating in calendar year 2019 or 2020 from ITEs, polytechnics, universities, or other educational institutions (e.g. private universities and overseas institutions); or
  Graduated earlier from above institutions and completed National Service in 2019 or 2020.
